If you want to run manually,
	1. Run POX controller. Go to directory 'application' and type 'make app' in the command line.
	2. Run Mininet. Open a new terminal and go to directory 'topology' and type 'make topo' in the command line.

If you want to test automatically,
	1. Run POX controller. Go to directory 'application' and type 'make app' in the command line.
	2. Run Mininet. Open a new terminal and go to directory 'topology' and type 'make topo' in the command line. The results will be generated automatically, named as 'phase_1_report' and stored in directory 'results'.
